					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p32668">True behavior of $2003/$2004 or FCE Ultra eccentricity?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=32668#p32668"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Apr 12, 2008 10:54 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
