			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It is possible to DMA from PRG-ROM or RAM to CHR-RAM or VRAM (must be external VRAM) through a mapper. Depending on how it's constructed you don't even need to halt the CPU. It's not a cheap feature to add though since either a ton of I/O are required to multiplex two memories, or a FPGA with sufficient block RAM is required.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
