					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That's basically what happens in the MMC5's EXRAM--- there is no such thing as DMA - but the RAM is shared between both buses.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Life is complex: it has both real and imaginary components.</div>
